{"tid":1790202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大對中共硬起來, 請求美國將「加拿大政治犯」納入貿易談判中","createTime":"2019-12-19T23:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T04:39:18.000Z","uid":134071,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e2bbd6d6e76fa8353cefec6a1c66d2e4638624da","tid":1790202,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T23:58:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498686-20191220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498686-20191220.htm&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Qmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=3ba19d94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498686-20191220.htm&h=ca41fd18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498686-20191220.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n 杜魯多：若兩公民未獲釋 美國不應與中國簽署全面協議<br />\n2019-12-20 HKT 07:16<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>加拿大總理杜魯多表示，除非兩名被中國當局拘捕的加拿大人獲得釋放，否則美國政府不應與中國簽署最終及全面的貿易協議。</strong><br />\n<br />\n加拿大警方在去年12月拘捕中國電信商華為副董事長孟晚舟之後，中國當局先後拘捕加拿大商人邁克爾及前外交官康明凱。<br />\n<br />\n杜魯多表示，加拿大一直與華盛頓合作，以說服中國釋放兩人，若果解決不了孟晚舟及兩名加拿大人的問題，美國不應與中國簽署全面的經貿協議。"},{"pid":"5a4ff16571e72f591979f1d3e7e32bf3b9acba40","tid":1790202,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T23:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91ddc4254207508cfd66959713a22c594db013f","tid":1790202,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T00:19:43.000Z","msg":"支那人點會講得通 左膠"},{"pid":"3777f7e937eb12e4e2355e380edcb2d7de16d998","tid":1790202,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T00:24:51.000Z","msg":"Trudeau<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a28793a515bb4ff8e0866ac61bd373303b380c","tid":1790202,"uid":292710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a4ff16571e72f591979f1d3e